02/12/2004
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- High Representative Paddy Ashdown and BiH presidency member Sulejman Tihic signed an agreement Wednesday (1 December) establishing the Registry Office Division I for War Crimes and Division II for Organised Crime, Crime in Economy and Corruption of the BiH Court.
Afterwards, Tihic said it was an important move that will allow the creation of an efficient and independent judiciary in BiH and the prosecution of serious criminal acts, especially those involving war crimes and organised crime.
(Nezavisne Novine, Dnevni Avaz - 02/12/04;
FENA - 01/12/04)
